description: This dazzling truck is bringing authentic and delicious Venezuelan street cuisine to the ravenous foodies of Dallas. After serving the streets of Venezuela for many years, this talented team made their way to Texas so that they could share their fantastic fare with eager new eaters. Everyone is loving their their pepitos (Venezuelan-style hero sandwiches) and arepas because they’re positively stuffed to perfection with scrumptious meats and cheeses.Once you try a taste of any of these meals, you too will see that it’s impossible for your appetite not to be pleased.
name: Meat In The Street
